longBusinessSummary: Eurotech, Ltd., a development stage company, engages in acquiring, developing, and marketing chemical and electronic technologies for use in environmental and security sectors. The company's portfolio of technology products include proprietary materials to solves the problems of how nuclear and other hazardous wastes are contained; and performance materials for use in industrial products, such as coatings and paints. It also provides Web based technologies for online video streaming, distribution, and networking. Eurotech, Ltd. is based in Manassas, Virginia.
